		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Please learn how to program before taking on more projects. If you cannot figure out Zelda's "effect" of type writer text display, how can you possibly accomplish anything? As Celius pointed out, you use a timer to direct updates and you track through the string until completed. It's not hard to figure out at all.

		

		</td>
