	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />You could probably just calculate a hash from the character, then use it as the delay (so a particular character always delays the same). Or just randomly delay, as the player will probably not notice. Many games make a sound only for non-space characters, and some even add delays as a more dramatic punctuation (probably embedded with an escape code in the string).

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


